rank: #1 in Best Colleges in New Jersey
description:
editorial
Princeton is an elite private university located in Princeton, New Jersey. It is a mid-size institution with an enrollment of 5,540 undergraduate students. Admissions is extremely competitive as the Princeton acceptance rate is only 6%. Popular majors include Computer Science, Economics, and Public Policy Analysis. Graduating 97% of students, Princeton alumni go on to earn a starting salary of $60,800.
